Package: SC2P
Title: Two phase differential expression for single-cell RNA-seq
Version: 1.0.3
Author: Zhijin (Jean) Wu <zwu@stat.brown.edu>, Jamie (Yi) Zhang <yi_zhang@brown.edu>, Hao Wu<hao.wu@emory.edu>
Maintainer: Zhijin (Jean) Wu <zwu@stat.brown.edu>, Hao Wu <hao.wu@emory.edu>
Description: This package performs differential expression analysis for singel-cell RNA-seq
			 data in two phases: phase transition (probability of being expressed),
			 and magnitude tuning (levels of expression once the gene is on).
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), Biobase, limma
License: GPL
biocViews: Sequencing, RNASeq, DifferentialExpression
